{
  "stem": "1765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were placed-- when the government tells you you have to take somebody in, you just do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to take in what was called the village bum later on-- Vanya the bum-- when we had our own little hut.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were assigned to this family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was assigned also, by-- everything was assigned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The communist government gave people no choice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mula Rudomin went to work as a bookkeeper, and Raja Rudomin went to work in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandmother was too old to work any kind of a job, and I went to school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was assigned to a school, and that's where I went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From that first hut, it wasn't very far.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was maybe a 15 minute walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Other schools-- another school I went to there, I had a very long walk through snowy storms and bad weather.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this was fairly close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a [NON-ENGLISH] school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a-- the elementary school or the-- for all I know it was the school for the whole-- for the whole village.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Michael-- Mikhail Gorbachev's wife, Lisa Gorbachev, grew up in Rubtsovsk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sure we went to the same school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She's two years younger than I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't believe it when someone said that she grew up in Rubtsovsk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in her autobiography, indeed it says that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was our first Fall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Autumn.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russian, and I didn't-- I came to Russia without knowing Russian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew Polish and Yiddish, so I was illiterate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very hard, but still, compared to what was happening to my cousins, it was minor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But to me, at that time, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, the Sh-- the Holocaust has many faces, and everything is relative.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
